      "writtenOn": "2020-04-23T01:17:24Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Ideally you’d say something about which task it is, to help trace it.\n\n    LOG(ERROR) \u003c\u003c \"task 0x\" \u003c\u003c std::hex \u003c\u003c task \u003c\u003c \" !\u003d 0x\" \u003c\u003c mach_task_self();\n\nor the base::StringPrintf-ed equivalent.",
